<font color="#ffff00"><b>Hey, guys. Are you guys looking for me?</b></font>

9
00:01:43,243 --> 00:01:45,083
<font color="#ffff00"><b>-Where's Shancai?
-Shancai?</b></font>

10
00:01:46,203 --> 00:01:47,683
<font color="#ffff00"><b>She didn't come to our previous class.</b></font>

11
00:01:49,043 --> 00:01:50,363
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I'm not sure what happened to her.</b></font>

12
00:01:50,603 --> 00:01:53,203
<font color="#ffff00"><b>She's also not answering her phone.
That's not like her at all.</b></font>

13
00:01:54,323 --> 00:01:55,843
<font color="#ffff00"><b>When was the last time you saw her?</b></font>

14
00:01:57,043 --> 00:02:00,563
<font color="#ffff00"><b>After class earlier,
she left with Shunping.</b></font>

15
00:02:02,323 --> 00:02:03,163
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Shunping?</b></font>

16
00:02:03,243 --> 00:02:05,403
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Yes. He's our high school
classmate's brother, Zhibu.</b></font>

17
00:02:06,163 --> 00:02:08,843
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I see. Let us know
when Shancai comes back, Xiaoqing.</b></font>

18
00:02:09,923 --> 00:02:10,883
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Sure.</b></font>

19
00:02:13,243 --> 00:02:15,363
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Don't call me Xiaoqing anymore.</b></font>

20
00:02:27,643 --> 00:02:28,483
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Hello?</b></font>

21
00:02:28,843 --> 00:02:31,443
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>Qinghe, didn't I tell you to call me
when Shancai gets back?</i></b></font>

22
00:02:31,683 --> 00:02:32,683
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>I've waited all afternoon.</i></b></font>

23
00:02:32,803 --> 00:02:35,123
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I didn't forget. Shancai
didn't come to class all afternoon.</b></font>

24
00:02:36,003 --> 00:02:38,323
<font color="#ffff00"><b>And I couldn't reach her phone.
I'm not sure where she went.</b></font>

25
00:02:39,363 --> 00:02:40,283
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>Come here now.</i></b></font>

26
00:02:41,243 --> 00:02:42,123
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Okay.</b></font>

27
00:02:42,403 --> 00:02:43,403
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I'll be right over.</b></font>

28
00:02:47,963 --> 00:02:50,123
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Shancai didn't come back
the whole afternoon.</b></font>

29
00:02:51,443 --> 00:02:52,323
<font color="#ffff00"><b>That's so unlike her.</b></font>

30
00:02:53,123 --> 00:02:54,163
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I think something happened.</b></font>

31
00:02:54,843 --> 00:02:57,643
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Do you remember who Qinghe said
Shancai left with earlier?</b></font>

32
00:02:58,123 --> 00:03:01,043
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Apparently, the guy's name is Shunping.</b></font>

33
00:03:01,323 --> 00:03:02,643
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I'll go ask the office about him.</b></font>

34
00:03:11,403 --> 00:03:12,803
<font color="#ffff00"><b>-All right, Ximen.
-Hey.</b></font>

35
00:03:12,963 --> 00:03:14,323
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Were you able to contact Shancai?</b></font>

36
00:03:14,883 --> 00:03:17,403
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Ximen called earlier
and said that Shunping</b></font>

37
00:03:17,883 --> 00:03:19,323
<font color="#ffff00"><b>has dropped out of Mingde University.</b></font>

38
00:03:22,683 --> 00:03:25,123
<font color="#ffff00"><b>But he came to see Shancai this morning.</b></font>

39
00:03:26,803 --> 00:03:28,003
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I don't feel good about this.</b></font>

40
00:03:28,603 --> 00:03:31,043
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You said that your high school classmate
is Shunping's brother.</b></font>

41
00:03:31,123 --> 00:03:32,163
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Do you have his number?</b></font>

42
00:03:33,523 --> 00:03:34,363
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Let me see.</b></font>

43
00:03:35,003 --> 00:03:37,003
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Si's phone is turned off.</b></font>

44
00:03:39,043 --> 00:03:40,403
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Yan Zhibu's phone is ringing.</b></font>

45
00:03:42,443 --> 00:03:43,283
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Hello?</b></font>

46
00:03:43,523 --> 00:03:44,923
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Are you Yan Zhibu?</b></font>

47
00:03:57,283 --> 00:03:58,923
<font color="#ffff00"><b>-You're here.
-Mr. Liu, is Si home?</b></font>

48
00:04:00,763 --> 00:04:03,203
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Si sits in the library
every time he comes home.</b></font>

49
00:04:04,283 --> 00:04:05,483
<font color="#ffff00"><b>He doesn't look happy.</b></font>

50
00:04:06,043 --> 00:04:07,043
<font color="#ffff00"><b>What does he do in there?</b></font>

51
00:04:07,683 --> 00:04:08,883
<font color="#ffff00"><b>He checks the stock market</b></font>

52
00:04:09,163 --> 00:04:10,123
<font color="#ffff00"><b>or reads books.</b></font>

53
00:04:10,443 --> 00:04:11,963
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Or plays games or takes naps.</b></font>

54
00:04:12,523 --> 00:04:14,243
<font color="#ffff00"><b>He doesn't want to speak to anyone.</b></font>

55
00:04:48,003 --> 00:04:48,883
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Boss.</b></font>

56
00:04:49,603 --> 00:04:50,483
<font color="#ffff00"><b>She's awake.</b></font>

57
00:04:55,563 --> 00:04:56,563
<font color="#ffff00"><b>What are you doing?</b></font>

58
00:04:57,803 --> 00:04:58,923
<font color="#ffff00"><b>What are you doing?</b></font>

59
00:05:04,683 --> 00:05:07,323
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Stop struggling.
You won't be able to escape.</b></font>

60
00:05:10,163 --> 00:05:11,003
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Boss.</b></font>

61
00:05:11,563 --> 00:05:12,403
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Let's do it.</b></font>

62
00:05:12,723 --> 00:05:15,203
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Be patient. Let's take her picture first.</b></font>

63
00:05:19,083 --> 00:05:20,003
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Stop moving around.</b></font>

64
00:05:29,603 --> 00:05:30,443
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Boss.</b></font>

65
00:05:30,763 --> 00:05:32,323
<font color="#ffff00"><b>She doesn't look pitiful enough.</b></font>

66
00:05:35,203 --> 00:05:36,283
<font color="#ffff00"><b>One more shot.</b></font>

67
00:05:40,123 --> 00:05:42,763
<font color="#ffff00"><b>No. I don't think
now is the best time to sell it.</b></font>

68
00:05:43,123 --> 00:05:45,323
<font color="#ffff00"><b>-I still want to wait. And tomorrow--
-Si.</b></font>

69
00:05:49,883 --> 00:05:52,643
<font color="#ffff00"><b>-What's up? Did something happen?
-Why won't you answer your phone?</b></font>

70
00:05:54,563 --> 00:05:56,363
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I'm not in the mood. What happened?</b></font>

71
00:05:57,563 --> 00:05:58,643
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Shancai's missing.</b></font>

72
00:06:05,163 --> 00:06:06,003
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Boss.</b></font>

73
00:06:08,483 --> 00:06:10,043
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Shunping, you're here.</b></font>

74
00:06:20,243 --> 00:06:21,083
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Boss.</b></font>

75
00:06:21,403 --> 00:06:22,963
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Why did you tie Shancai up?</b></font>

76
00:06:25,843 --> 00:06:26,683
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Shunping.</b></font>

77
00:06:27,043 --> 00:06:28,043
<font color="#ffff00"><b>What are you doing?</b></font>

78
00:06:29,843 --> 00:06:33,403
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Shunping, we did that just in case...</b></font>

79
00:06:34,083 --> 00:06:35,123
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Boss, I don't get it.</b></font>

80
00:06:35,643 --> 00:06:38,643
<font color="#ffff00"><b>This was not the plan when you asked me
to approach Shancai before.</b></font>

81
00:06:40,723 --> 00:06:41,883
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Boss.</b></font>

82
00:06:42,003 --> 00:06:45,523
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Do you remember Daoming Si,
the one who broke your leg?</b></font>

83
00:06:48,123 --> 00:06:49,323
<font color="#ffff00"><b>How can I forget?</b></font>

84
00:06:50,083 --> 00:06:51,963
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Why? Did you see him?</b></font>

85
00:06:52,523 --> 00:06:53,923
<font color="#ffff00"><b>No, my brother did.</b></font>

86
00:06:54,843 --> 00:06:56,643
<font color="#ffff00"><b>He was beaten up by Daoming Si</b></font>

87
00:06:57,243 --> 00:06:59,763
<font color="#ffff00"><b>at his high school reunion two days ago.
He was even hospitalized.</b></font>

88
00:07:00,443 --> 00:07:01,643
<font color="#ffff00"><b>He was beaten up?</b></font>

89
00:07:01,723 --> 00:07:02,603
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Why?</b></font>

90
00:07:03,443 --> 00:07:06,003
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Apparently because of a girl
named Shancai.</b></font>

91
00:07:07,123 --> 00:07:08,563
<font color="#ffff00"><b>She's Daoming Si's girlfriend.</b></font>

92
00:07:08,803 --> 00:07:09,883
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Shunping.</b></font>

93
00:07:10,203 --> 00:07:13,003
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I think you should become friends
with that girl named Shancai.</b></font>

94
00:07:13,683 --> 00:07:16,843
<font color="#ffff00"><b>And convince her
not to be together with Daoming Si.</b></font>

95
00:07:19,283 --> 00:07:20,843
<font color="#ffff00"><b>All right.</b></font>

96
00:07:21,203 --> 00:07:22,043
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Thank you.</b></font>

97
00:07:22,883 --> 00:07:24,003
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Shunping?</b></font>

98
00:07:24,083 --> 00:07:25,963
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Shancai, we meet again.</b></font>

99
00:07:28,683 --> 00:07:29,523
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Shunping.</b></font>

100
00:07:30,003 --> 00:07:31,123
<font color="#ffff00"><b>What happened to your face?</b></font>

101
00:07:33,443 --> 00:07:35,043
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I had an encounter with Daoming Si today.</b></font>

102
00:07:36,723 --> 00:07:37,563
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Tell me about it.</b></font>

103
00:07:37,723 --> 00:07:38,603
<font color="#ffff00"><b>What happened?</b></font>

104
00:07:40,043 --> 00:07:42,363
<font color="#ffff00"><b>That guy is too arrogant and dominating.</b></font>

105
00:07:43,123 --> 00:07:44,923
<font color="#ffff00"><b>He doesn't know how Shancai feels.</b></font>

106
00:07:48,323 --> 00:07:50,483
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I couldn't contain myself
so we had a fight.</b></font>

107
00:07:52,763 --> 00:07:56,443
<font color="#ffff00"><b>He was also very arrogant and dominating
when I met him before.</b></font>

108
00:07:57,123 --> 00:07:58,723
<font color="#ffff00"><b>He's so annoying.</b></font>

109
00:08:00,163 --> 00:08:02,403
<font color="#ffff00"><b>That kind of person
needs to be taught a lesson.</b></font>

110
00:08:04,323 --> 00:08:07,523
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Shunping, can you arrange for me
to meet Shancai tomorrow?</b></font>

111
00:08:08,843 --> 00:08:10,763
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Sure. But why?</b></font>

112
00:08:11,323 --> 00:08:13,483
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Nothing.
I just want to have a chat with her.</b></font>

113
00:08:14,363 --> 00:08:16,683
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Maybe I can convince her
to leave Daoming Si soon.</b></font>

114
00:08:18,643 --> 00:08:19,483
<font color="#ffff00"><b>That's a good idea.</b></font>

115
00:08:20,163 --> 00:08:21,563
<font color="#ffff00"><b>-I'll set it up.
-Okay.</b></font>

116
00:08:31,243 --> 00:08:33,243
<font color="#ffff00"><b>How did Daoming Si treat boss before?</b></font>

117
00:08:34,203 --> 00:08:35,323
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Have you forgotten?</b></font>

118
00:08:37,883 --> 00:08:40,043
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Shunping, do you plan to betray us?</b></font>

119
00:08:42,483 --> 00:08:43,683
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Of course not.</b></font>

120
00:08:44,923 --> 00:08:46,043
<font color="#ffff00"><b>A person like Daoming Si</b></font>

121
00:08:46,523 --> 00:08:48,003
<font color="#ffff00"><b>doesn't deserve to be forgiven.</b></font>

122
00:08:50,003 --> 00:08:51,323
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Boss' leg</b></font>

123
00:08:52,723 --> 00:08:54,123
<font color="#ffff00"><b>was crippled because of Daoming Si.</b></font>

124
00:08:57,243 --> 00:09:00,163
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I've already taken a photo.
I'll send it to Daoming Si.</b></font>

125
00:09:06,163 --> 00:09:07,163
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>He lied to me.</i></b></font>

126
00:09:07,243 --> 00:09:10,483
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>Shunping, who said he wanted
to be friends with me,</i> <i>to protect me,</i></b></font>

127
00:09:10,923 --> 00:09:12,003
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>lied to me.</i></b></font>

128
00:09:12,723 --> 00:09:14,003
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>Why did this happen?</i></b></font>

129
00:09:16,883 --> 00:09:17,723
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Boss.</b></font>

130
00:09:18,323 --> 00:09:20,523
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I want to talk to her alone.</b></font>

131
00:09:21,123 --> 00:09:22,083
<font color="#ffff00"><b>May I?</b></font>

132
00:09:24,843 --> 00:09:25,763
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Don't worry.</b></font>

133
00:09:26,243 --> 00:09:27,283
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I won't let her go.</b></font>

134
00:09:28,523 --> 00:09:29,363
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Don't forget.</b></font>

135
00:09:32,443 --> 00:09:33,723
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I'm on your side.</b></font>

136
00:09:34,883 --> 00:09:35,723
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Sure.</b></font>

137
00:09:36,403 --> 00:09:37,323
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Don't take too long.</b></font>

138
00:09:38,003 --> 00:09:38,963
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Okay.</b></font>

139
00:09:56,643 --> 00:09:57,483
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Why?</b></font>

140
00:09:57,963 --> 00:09:58,923
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Why?</b></font>

141
00:10:02,523 --> 00:10:03,443
<font color="#ffff00"><b>For what?</b></font>

142
00:10:20,243 --> 00:10:21,203
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Why are you doing this?</b></font>

143
00:10:22,363 --> 00:10:23,563
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I trusted you.</b></font>

144
00:10:24,683 --> 00:10:25,723
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Why?</b></font>

145
00:10:26,763 --> 00:10:27,603
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Liar.</b></font>

146
00:10:28,083 --> 00:10:29,083
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Jerk!</b></font>

147
00:10:29,203 --> 00:10:30,163
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Scum!</b></font>

148
00:10:31,283 --> 00:10:32,403
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Say whatever you want.</b></font>

149
00:10:33,363 --> 00:10:34,563
<font color="#ffff00"><b>If that makes you feel better,</b></font>

150
00:10:36,003 --> 00:10:36,883
<font color="#ffff00"><b>do it.</b></font>

151
00:10:40,243 --> 00:10:42,043
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Why are you doing this?</b></font>

152
00:10:45,043 --> 00:10:48,083
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I think boss wants to use you
to deal with Daoming Si.</b></font>

153
00:10:49,763 --> 00:10:51,483
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Daoming Si crippled his leg.</b></font>

154
00:10:52,403 --> 00:10:54,123
<font color="#ffff00"><b>He needs to pay for it.</b></font>

155
00:10:59,323 --> 00:11:00,683
<font color="#ffff00"><b>When I was in junior high school,</b></font>

156
00:11:02,763 --> 00:11:04,483
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I didn't like to be in school.</b></font>

157
00:11:05,363 --> 00:11:07,883
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I didn't like being with that stupid Zhibu
at home even more.</b></font>

158
00:11:10,123 --> 00:11:11,843
<font color="#ffff00"><b>So I went out and did some part-time job.</b></font>

159
00:11:13,603 --> 00:11:15,083
<font color="#ffff00"><b>But I also got into a lot of trouble.</b></font>

160
00:11:17,763 --> 00:11:20,763
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I met boss at a bar later on.</b></font>

161
00:11:21,763 --> 00:11:23,243
<font color="#ffff00"><b>He helped me with my problems.</b></font>

162
00:11:23,803 --> 00:11:25,843
<font color="#ffff00"><b>And he even convinced me
to go back to school.</b></font>

163
00:11:27,083 --> 00:11:27,963
<font color="#ffff00"><b>And then one day,</b></font>

164
00:11:29,003 --> 00:11:31,163
<font color="#ffff00"><b>that arrogant guy, Daoming Si,</b></font>

165
00:11:31,603 --> 00:11:33,923
<font color="#ffff00"><b>argued with boss at a bar.</b></font>

166
00:11:35,963 --> 00:11:38,043
<font color="#ffff00"><b>He said boss is a rascal
and that he's useless.</b></font>

167
00:11:41,683 --> 00:11:44,003
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Boss and his men got mad
and had a fight with Daoming Si.</b></font>

168
00:11:45,483 --> 00:11:46,883
<font color="#ffff00"><b>But Daoming Si went crazy</b></font>

169
00:11:48,083 --> 00:11:49,403
<font color="#ffff00"><b>and beat everyone up.</b></font>

170
00:11:50,963 --> 00:11:51,843
<font color="#ffff00"><b>He also broke...</b></font>

171
00:11:53,403 --> 00:11:54,603
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Boss' leg.</b></font>

172
00:11:57,763 --> 00:11:58,923
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Because of that,</b></font>

173
00:12:00,203 --> 00:12:01,843
<font color="#ffff00"><b>everyone got arrested by the police,</b></font>

174
00:12:02,843 --> 00:12:04,163
<font color="#ffff00"><b>even Daoming Si.</b></font>

175
00:12:06,083 --> 00:12:07,243
<font color="#ffff00"><b>But boss's leg</b></font>

176
00:12:07,923 --> 00:12:09,523
<font color="#ffff00"><b>would never ever recover.</b></font>

177
00:12:10,923 --> 00:12:12,883
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Shouldn't Daoming Si
take responsibility for this?</b></font>

178
00:12:22,203 --> 00:12:23,043
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Shunping.</b></font>

179
00:12:24,563 --> 00:12:26,163
<font color="#ffff00"><b>What you're doing is against the law.</b></font>

180
00:12:27,123 --> 00:12:29,323
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You'll be expelled by the school.
Do you know that?</b></font>

181
00:12:31,403 --> 00:12:33,043
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Even though I got into Mingde University,</b></font>

182
00:12:34,283 --> 00:12:37,323
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I couldn't take
the pressure of the competition.</b></font>

183
00:12:37,883 --> 00:12:39,483
<font color="#ffff00"><b>It seems like everyone is doing better</b></font>

184
00:12:40,763 --> 00:12:41,963
<font color="#ffff00"><b>than me.</b></font>

185
00:12:44,363 --> 00:12:46,043
<font color="#ffff00"><b>That's why I dropped out a long time ago.</b></font>

186
00:12:55,923 --> 00:12:57,883
<font color="#ffff00"><b>So you approached me on purpose</b></font>

187
00:12:59,163 --> 00:13:00,963
<font color="#ffff00"><b>in order to avenge boss?</b></font>

