<font color="#ffff00"><b>I'm not who I was anymore.</b></font>

376
00:26:28,163 --> 00:26:29,243
<font color="#ffff00"><b>What was he like before?</b></font>

377
00:26:34,163 --> 00:26:36,763
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Huaze Lei. How was Daoming Si before?</b></font>

378
00:26:38,843 --> 00:26:41,403
<font color="#ffff00"><b>The old Daoming Si was quite absurd.</b></font>

379
00:26:42,003 --> 00:26:42,923
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Absurd?</b></font>

380
00:26:43,363 --> 00:26:45,003
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Isn't he also quite absurd now?</b></font>

381
00:26:45,643 --> 00:26:46,843
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Compared to how he used to be,</b></font>

382
00:26:47,403 --> 00:26:48,363
<font color="#ffff00"><b>the new Si</b></font>

383
00:26:48,723 --> 00:26:52,203
<font color="#ffff00"><b>is Mr. Virtue.</b></font>

384
00:26:55,723 --> 00:26:58,643
<font color="#ffff00"><b>What are you looking at?
You're lucky you met the new me.</b></font>

385
00:26:59,803 --> 00:27:00,683
<font color="#ffff00"><b>That's right.</b></font>

386
00:27:00,763 --> 00:27:03,563
<font color="#ffff00"><b>The old Si always looked for trouble.
And he was never motivated.</b></font>

387
00:27:03,643 --> 00:27:05,763
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Good thing we were able to change him.</b></font>

388
00:27:06,243 --> 00:27:08,523
<font color="#ffff00"><b>We helped him study
at the library every day.</b></font>

389
00:27:08,603 --> 00:27:10,523
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Good thing that he's naturally smart.</b></font>

390
00:27:10,683 --> 00:27:12,683
<font color="#ffff00"><b>He got into Mingde University
with a very high score.</b></font>

391
00:27:14,163 --> 00:27:15,803
<font color="#ffff00"><b>He got into Mingde University indeed.</b></font>

392
00:27:16,283 --> 00:27:18,723
<font color="#ffff00"><b>But he's not naturally that smart.</b></font>

393
00:27:20,763 --> 00:27:21,603
<font color="#ffff00"><b>All right.</b></font>

394
00:27:21,883 --> 00:27:24,243
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Are you planning to talk
about my past all night?</b></font>

395
00:27:25,723 --> 00:27:27,763
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You ungrateful guy.</b></font>

396
00:27:27,843 --> 00:27:29,923
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You forgot all the times
we were with you before.</b></font>

397
00:27:30,003 --> 00:27:30,843
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You...</b></font>

398
00:27:31,203 --> 00:27:32,643
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Never mind. Let's go.</b></font>

399
00:27:32,723 --> 00:27:34,563
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Let's give them some quality time.</b></font>

400
00:27:34,643 --> 00:27:35,483
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Bye.</b></font>

401
00:27:58,843 --> 00:28:00,043
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Why aren't you saying anything?</b></font>

402
00:28:03,323 --> 00:28:05,883
<font color="#ffff00"><b>What's with that attitude?
Is that how you treat a patient?</b></font>

403
00:28:07,803 --> 00:28:09,563
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Do you think you're so great?</b></font>

404
00:28:09,643 --> 00:28:11,323
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Why was I so nosy that I risked my life</b></font>

405
00:28:11,523 --> 00:28:14,403
<font color="#ffff00"><b>and got hurt all over just to save
an ungrateful and stupid girl like you?</b></font>

406
00:28:14,923 --> 00:28:17,203
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You're the stupid one.
You even dare to say that to me.</b></font>

407
00:28:17,403 --> 00:28:18,963
<font color="#ffff00"><b>If you didn't cause trouble before,</b></font>

408
00:28:19,203 --> 00:28:20,203
<font color="#ffff00"><b>how would you get hurt?</b></font>

409
00:28:21,963 --> 00:28:23,683
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Cut it out. Stop babbling.</b></font>

410
00:28:23,803 --> 00:28:25,643
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You just know how to fight
with people all day.</b></font>

411
00:28:25,843 --> 00:28:28,403
<font color="#ffff00"><b>-Don't you know how to comfort a patient?
-Because...</b></font>

412
00:28:46,443 --> 00:28:47,283
<font color="#ffff00"><b>What...</b></font>

413
00:28:47,803 --> 00:28:48,683
<font color="#ffff00"><b>What are you doing?</b></font>

414
00:28:52,603 --> 00:28:54,083
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Because I had a dream.</b></font>

415
00:28:56,483 --> 00:28:57,483
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I dreamt that you died.</b></font>

416
00:28:59,323 --> 00:29:01,123
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Then I thought you really died.</b></font>

417
00:29:03,803 --> 00:29:06,003
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I thought you wouldn't come and save me</b></font>

418
00:29:06,603 --> 00:29:08,043
<font color="#ffff00"><b>because I said those things to you.</b></font>

419
00:29:09,803 --> 00:29:11,603
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I never thought you'd still come.</b></font>

420
00:29:13,563 --> 00:29:16,803
<font color="#ffff00"><b>And you got beaten up so badly
by those scums</b></font>

421
00:29:18,123 --> 00:29:19,123
<font color="#ffff00"><b>and turned out this way.</b></font>

422
00:29:24,723 --> 00:29:25,683
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Sorry.</b></font>

423
00:29:27,843 --> 00:29:30,163
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Stop looking like that.
You're already ugly as it is.</b></font>

424
00:29:32,563 --> 00:29:33,563
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Didn't I tell you before?</b></font>

425
00:29:34,043 --> 00:29:36,003
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Even if you went to Mars,
I'd still go after you.</b></font>

426
00:29:36,363 --> 00:29:38,403
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You wouldn't be able to get rid
of me in this life.</b></font>

427
00:29:38,883 --> 00:29:40,443
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Stop struggling for no reason.</b></font>

428
00:29:43,203 --> 00:29:44,123
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Stupid boy.</b></font>

429
00:29:45,883 --> 00:29:48,563
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Your face is so ugly right now.
Are you planning to laugh or cry?</b></font>

430
00:29:48,923 --> 00:29:50,043
<font color="#ffff00"><b>It's none of your business.</b></font>

431
00:30:00,963 --> 00:30:03,963
<font color="#ffff00"><b>It's good that they came back safely
even though they were hurt this time.</b></font>

432
00:30:04,643 --> 00:30:05,723
<font color="#ffff00"><b>But it was really dangerous.</b></font>

433
00:30:06,363 --> 00:30:07,203
<font color="#ffff00"><b>That's right.</b></font>

434
00:30:07,483 --> 00:30:09,763
<font color="#ffff00"><b>If you think about it now,
we almost weren't able to change</b></font>

435
00:30:10,003 --> 00:30:11,363
<font color="#ffff00"><b>the old Si.</b></font>

436
00:30:12,563 --> 00:30:14,443
<font color="#ffff00"><b>There were times when
we almost fought with him.</b></font>

437
00:30:14,763 --> 00:30:16,083
<font color="#ffff00"><b>It's good we didn't give up.</b></font>

438
00:30:16,883 --> 00:30:18,083
<font color="#ffff00"><b>How could we give up on him?</b></font>

439
00:30:18,803 --> 00:30:19,963
<font color="#ffff00"><b>He has helped us a lot.</b></font>

440
00:30:21,083 --> 00:30:22,843
<font color="#ffff00"><b>We can't let this kind of thing
happen again.</b></font>

441
00:30:24,403 --> 00:30:27,283
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Even though he's very headstrong now,
he has learned to respect himself</b></font>

442
00:30:27,563 --> 00:30:29,043
<font color="#ffff00"><b>because he found someone he loves.</b></font>

443
00:30:41,643 --> 00:30:42,483
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Hey.</b></font>

444
00:30:44,163 --> 00:30:45,003
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Who are you?</b></font>

445
00:30:50,083 --> 00:30:52,163
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I'm Shunping, the one who beat up
Daoming Si so badly.</b></font>

446
00:31:01,283 --> 00:31:03,483
<font color="#ffff00"><b>What? You want me to come visit you daily?</b></font>

447
00:31:03,643 --> 00:31:05,563
<font color="#ffff00"><b>-No way.
-Why not?</b></font>

448
00:31:05,643 --> 00:31:07,923
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I need to work. How will I have the time?</b></font>

449
00:31:08,483 --> 00:31:11,123
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You ungrateful woman.
I'll double your salary. Come here.</b></font>

450
00:31:11,803 --> 00:31:13,803
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Don't always use money to buy people.</b></font>

451
00:31:13,963 --> 00:31:15,603
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You morally-corrupt bum.</b></font>

452
00:31:16,363 --> 00:31:18,243
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Then how would you repay me? Tell me.</b></font>

453
00:31:19,163 --> 00:31:20,003
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Shut it.</b></font>

454
00:31:20,363 --> 00:31:21,723
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Lie down and rest.</b></font>

455
00:31:32,643 --> 00:31:33,603
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Why are you here?</b></font>

456
00:31:35,403 --> 00:31:36,643
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Haven't you done enough?</b></font>

457
00:31:38,523 --> 00:31:39,683
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Why are you here?</b></font>

458
00:31:41,923 --> 00:31:44,763
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Your friends are all by the door.
What can I do to you?</b></font>

459
00:31:45,363 --> 00:31:46,243
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Don't worry.</b></font>

460
00:31:46,803 --> 00:31:47,683
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Shancai.</b></font>

461
00:31:48,563 --> 00:31:49,723
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Before I surrender myself,</b></font>

462
00:31:50,683 --> 00:31:52,203
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I want to apologize to you.</b></font>

463
00:32:07,763 --> 00:32:09,403
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Boss was already arrested</b></font>

464
00:32:10,483 --> 00:32:11,883
<font color="#ffff00"><b>because of what we did to you.</b></font>

465
00:32:12,523 --> 00:32:15,603
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I'll also surrender myself for what I did
and accept my punishment.</b></font>

466
00:32:16,323 --> 00:32:17,323
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I'm really sorry.</b></font>

467
00:32:20,443 --> 00:32:21,923
<font color="#ffff00"><b>It's too late to apologize now.</b></font>

468
00:32:22,323 --> 00:32:23,323
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Get out.</b></font>

469
00:32:32,203 --> 00:32:33,203
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Shancai.</b></font>

470
00:32:35,603 --> 00:32:37,483
<font color="#ffff00"><b>If you're not the girl Daoming Si likes,</b></font>

471
00:32:38,763 --> 00:32:42,243
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I'd hope we can become good friends.</b></font>

472
00:32:48,163 --> 00:32:49,083
<font color="#ffff00"><b>It's really a shame.</b></font>

473
00:33:01,123 --> 00:33:02,723
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I originally wanted to beat him up.</b></font>

474
00:33:03,363 --> 00:33:05,763
<font color="#ffff00"><b>But I'm not mad anymore
after seeing his pathetic face.</b></font>

475
00:33:06,483 --> 00:33:08,043
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You still want to beat people up?</b></font>

476
00:33:08,123 --> 00:33:10,643
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Ouch! You violent girl.
Why did you hit me where I'm hurt?</b></font>

477
00:33:11,483 --> 00:33:13,723
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Sorry. I didn't do it on purpose.</b></font>

478
00:33:19,363 --> 00:33:20,243
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I...</b></font>

479
00:33:20,483 --> 00:33:22,243
<font color="#ffff00"><b>This is the most touching love story.</b></font>

480
00:33:22,363 --> 00:33:24,163
<font color="#ffff00"><b>A firm and unyielding man like Daoming Si</b></font>

481
00:33:24,363 --> 00:33:27,243
<font color="#ffff00"><b>risked his life for the woman he loves.</b></font>

482
00:33:27,643 --> 00:33:30,763
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Shancai, you must've done a lot of good
in the past to get a man like Daoming Si.</b></font>

483
00:33:31,003 --> 00:33:33,243
<font color="#ffff00"><b>This man is strong,
handsome and responsible.</b></font>

484
00:33:33,483 --> 00:33:35,083
<font color="#ffff00"><b>What do you think, Shancai?</b></font>

485
00:33:35,523 --> 00:33:36,563
<font color="#ffff00"><b>What do you mean?</b></font>

486
00:33:36,643 --> 00:33:38,483
<font color="#ffff00"><b>-Why are you telling me these things?
-Shancai.</b></font>

487
00:33:39,843 --> 00:33:40,763
<font color="#ffff00"><b>What do you want?</b></font>

488
00:33:40,883 --> 00:33:42,803
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I mean it.
You should treat each other well.</b></font>

489
00:33:43,363 --> 00:33:44,723
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You should help one another.</b></font>

490
00:33:45,003 --> 00:33:47,203
<font color="#ffff00"><b>That's right.
With a manly guy like Daoming Si,</b></font>

491
00:33:47,283 --> 00:33:49,643
<font color="#ffff00"><b>even if aliens came to Earth,
he would not let them hurt you.</b></font>

492
00:33:49,843 --> 00:33:52,203
<font color="#ffff00"><b>And Daoming Si is not right in the head.</b></font>

493
00:33:52,683 --> 00:33:54,443
<font color="#ffff00"><b>He won't look for another woman.</b></font>

494
00:33:55,163 --> 00:33:57,523
<font color="#ffff00"><b>He would risk his life and save you</b></font>

495
00:33:57,963 --> 00:34:00,123
<font color="#ffff00"><b>when you're in trouble.</b></font>

496
00:34:00,443 --> 00:34:01,883
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Stop it.</b></font>

497
00:34:01,963 --> 00:34:03,283
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I...</b></font>

498
00:34:03,363 --> 00:34:05,363
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Take this limited edition Daoming Si now.</b></font>

499
00:34:05,843 --> 00:34:07,643
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Even though his brain
doesn't work that well,</b></font>

500
00:34:07,763 --> 00:34:09,203
<font color="#ffff00"><b>you're not that smart yourself.</b></font>

501
00:34:09,483 --> 00:34:12,203
<font color="#ffff00"><b>-I think you suit each other.
-Hey.</b></font>

502
00:34:12,763 --> 00:34:13,683
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Don't come any closer.</b></font>

503
00:34:14,323 --> 00:34:18,043
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Shancai, don't you like
a manly guy like Daoming Si?</b></font>

504
00:34:18,523 --> 00:34:20,683
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Si is invincible.</b></font>

505
00:34:20,803 --> 00:34:21,643
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Hey.</b></font>

506
00:34:21,723 --> 00:34:23,803
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I'm manly too.</b></font>

507
00:34:24,163 --> 00:34:25,003
<font color="#ffff00"><b>And...</b></font>

508
00:34:26,643 --> 00:34:27,483
<font color="#ffff00"><b>But...</b></font>

509
00:34:29,083 --> 00:34:30,083
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Then...</b></font>

510
00:34:30,563 --> 00:34:32,283
<font color="#ffff00"><b>-Daoming Si is...
-Damn girl.</b></font>

511
00:34:32,363 --> 00:34:34,763
<font color="#ffff00"><b>What are you trying to say?</b></font>

512
00:34:36,283 --> 00:34:37,283
<font color="#ffff00"><b>And...</b></font>

513
00:34:37,523 --> 00:34:38,483
<font color="#ffff00"><b>But...</b></font>

514
00:34:38,563 --> 00:34:39,403
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Then...</b></font>

515
00:34:40,443 --> 00:34:41,323
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I think</b></font>

516
00:34:41,883 --> 00:34:42,723
<font color="#ffff00"><b>of Daoming Si...</b></font>

517
00:34:43,483 --> 00:34:45,123
<font color="#ffff00"><b>as a dog.</b></font>

518
00:34:48,803 --> 00:34:50,483
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Lei, stop laughing.</b></font>

519
00:34:51,043 --> 00:34:53,203
<font color="#ffff00"><b>But I can relate.</b></font>

520
00:34:53,363 --> 00:34:54,523
<font color="#ffff00"><b>A dog?</b></font>

521
00:34:55,883 --> 00:34:57,443
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Si, be strong.</b></font>

522
00:35:01,643 --> 00:35:03,203
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Of course we can't evade it.</b></font>

523
00:35:03,363 --> 00:35:04,683
<font color="#ffff00"><b>We have to face it head on.</b></font>

524
00:35:06,123 --> 00:35:08,443
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Mr. Wu, don't think too much.</b></font>

525
00:35:08,603 --> 00:35:10,043
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You won't suffer any losses.</b></font>

526
00:35:10,123 --> 00:35:13,763
<font color="#ffff00"><b>We prioritize the bonuses for our members.
You can't earn less even if you want to.</b></font>

527
00:35:14,283 --> 00:35:16,963
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Of course. You can find me
any time you call this number.</b></font>

528
00:35:17,283 --> 00:35:18,763
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I'll help you resolve your problems.</b></font>

529
00:35:22,083 --> 00:35:23,003
<font color="#ffff00"><b>That's good.</b></font>

530
00:35:23,403 --> 00:35:25,803
<font color="#ffff00"><b>It seems that your job
is going smoothly lately.</b></font>

531
00:35:27,363 --> 00:35:28,603
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I already have a plan.</b></font>

532
00:35:28,763 --> 00:35:31,603
<font color="#ffff00"><b>When I receive my first salary,
I'll add them to the stock immediately.</b></font>

533
00:35:32,323 --> 00:35:34,003
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Be careful.</b></font>

534
00:35:37,843 --> 00:35:39,963
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Is she still in the bathroom
after such a long time?</b></font>

535
00:35:40,523 --> 00:35:42,483
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Did you remind her not to get
her wounds wet?</b></font>

536
00:35:43,163 --> 00:35:44,163
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I did.</b></font>

537
00:35:46,203 --> 00:35:48,523
<font color="#ffff00"><b>We really have to thank
Daoming Si this time.</b></font>

538
00:35:48,843 --> 00:35:49,923
<font color="#ffff00"><b>He even got his face hurt</b></font>

539
00:35:50,203 --> 00:35:51,283
<font color="#ffff00"><b>to save Shancai.</b></font>

540
00:35:53,043 --> 00:35:55,603
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Shouldn't they settle the things
between them already?</b></font>

541
00:35:56,163 --> 00:35:57,683
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I think so too.</b></font>

542
00:35:59,763 --> 00:36:01,803
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Shancai, hurry.</b></font>

543
00:36:01,923 --> 00:36:03,363
<font color="#ffff00"><b>It's too humid in the bathroom.</b></font>

544
00:36:03,443 --> 00:36:05,203
<font color="#ffff00"><b>It's not good for your wounds.</b></font>

545
00:36:15,123 --> 00:36:16,603
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Congratulations on getting discharged.</b></font>

546
00:36:17,123 --> 00:36:20,243
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Si's recovers just like a dog.</b></font>

547
00:36:21,203 --> 00:36:22,043
<font color="#ffff00"><b>A dog?</b></font>

548
00:36:22,123 --> 00:36:24,123
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Don't mind being called a dog.
Dogs are nice.</b></font>

549
00:36:24,723 --> 00:36:27,203
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Maybe Shancai was complimenting you
for being as cute as a dog?</b></font>

550
00:36:28,843 --> 00:36:30,723
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Don't let me hear you say
the word "dog" again.</b></font>

551
00:36:31,043 --> 00:36:31,923
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Or else I'll kill you.</b></font>

552
00:36:37,243 --> 00:36:39,123
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I think you were really traumatized.</b></font>

553
00:36:41,603 --> 00:36:42,923
<font color="#ffff00"><b>How can you understand how I feel</b></font>

554
00:36:43,523 --> 00:36:44,883
<font color="#ffff00"><b>when the girl I risked my life for</b></font>

555
00:36:44,963 --> 00:36:46,003
<font color="#ffff00"><b>said,</b></font>

556
00:36:46,203 --> 00:36:48,203
<font color="#ffff00"><b>"I think of Daoming Si as a dog."</b></font>

557
00:36:51,923 --> 00:36:52,923
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>I think</i></b></font>

558
00:36:54,723 --> 00:36:55,763
<font color="#ffff00"><b>of Daoming Si...</b></font>

559
00:36:56,363 --> 00:36:57,683
<font color="#ffff00"><b>as a dog.</b></font>

560
00:37:01,243 --> 00:37:02,643
<font color="#ffff00"><b>She said I'm like a dog.</b></font>

561
00:37:04,203 --> 00:37:05,123
<font color="#ffff00"><b>That damn girl.</b></font>

562
00:37:06,723 --> 00:37:09,963
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I think Si is going to explode.</b></font>

563
00:37:13,563 --> 00:37:15,603
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I told you he shouldn't
be discharged so soon.</b></font>

564
00:37:19,603 --> 00:37:20,483
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I'm going to sleep.</b></font>

565
00:37:30,963 --> 00:37:33,723
<font color="#ffff00"><b>But Shancai is really stubborn.</b></font>

566
00:37:35,483 --> 00:37:37,243
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Innocent girls like her are annoying.</b></font>

567
00:37:38,083 --> 00:37:39,963
<font color="#ffff00"><b>They have
a lot of unrealistic expectations</b></font>

568
00:37:40,043 --> 00:37:41,683
<font color="#ffff00"><b>on relationships.</b></font>

569
00:37:44,123 --> 00:37:46,443
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Falling in love relies on</b></font>

570
00:37:47,003 --> 00:37:48,363
<font color="#ffff00"><b>that sudden feeling of love.</b></font>

571
00:37:51,323 --> 00:37:53,123
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Lei, what do you think?</b></font>

572
00:37:54,083 --> 00:37:54,923
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Me?</b></font>

573
00:37:55,883 --> 00:37:57,403
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I don't have any feelings at all.</b></font>

574
00:38:01,683 --> 00:38:03,483
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I think we're the only normal guys here.</b></font>

575
00:38:04,003 --> 00:38:05,083
<font color="#ffff00"><b>There's nothing we can do.</b></font>

576
00:38:05,163 --> 00:38:06,643
<font color="#ffff00"><b>We can only help Si</b></font>

577
00:38:06,883 --> 00:38:09,363
<font color="#ffff00"><b>make the innocent Shancai</b></font>

578
00:38:09,643 --> 00:38:10,483
<font color="#ffff00"><b>give in.</b></font>

579
00:38:29,123 --> 00:38:31,803
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Didn't you just get discharged?
Have you rested enough?</b></font>

580
00:38:31,883 --> 00:38:33,643
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Why are you in such a hurry
to come to school?</b></font>

581
00:38:33,723 --> 00:38:36,043
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I was afraid I won't be able to catch up.</b></font>

582
00:38:36,163 --> 00:38:38,803
<font color="#ffff00"><b>-I may have a lot to catch up later.
-I can lend you my notes.</b></font>

583
00:38:39,723 --> 00:38:40,563
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Thank you.</b></font>

584
00:38:40,883 --> 00:38:42,883
<font color="#ffff00"><b>But it's better for me to come to class.</b></font>

585
00:38:43,123 --> 00:38:44,563
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Shancai, are you all right?</b></font>

586
00:38:45,123 --> 00:38:46,523
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I wanted to visit you after class.</b></font>

587
00:38:46,683 --> 00:38:48,403
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Then give you my notes
for the past two days.</b></font>

588
00:38:48,923 --> 00:38:49,763
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Your notes?</b></font>

589
00:38:49,843 --> 00:38:51,803
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Your notes are useless.
Nobody can understand them.</b></font>

590
00:38:51,963 --> 00:38:53,643
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Shancai would be confused.</b></font>

591
00:38:53,763 --> 00:38:56,723
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I wrote my notes carefully for Shancai.</b></font>

592
00:38:57,563 --> 00:38:59,243
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Don't say things you don't know.</b></font>

593
00:39:00,643 --> 00:39:03,843
<font color="#ffff00"><b>All right. I need both of your notes.</b></font>

594
00:39:06,723 --> 00:39:08,683
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Shancai, is it okay
not to bandage your wound?</b></font>

595
00:39:10,683 --> 00:39:11,603
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I think it's fine.</b></font>

596
00:39:12,123 --> 00:39:13,843
<font color="#ffff00"><b>It feels fresher this way.</b></font>

597
00:39:17,723 --> 00:39:18,683
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Where's Daoming Si?</b></font>

598
00:39:19,243 --> 00:39:21,443
<font color="#ffff00"><b>He was discharged yesterday.
He's taking a sick day today.</b></font>

599
00:39:21,523 --> 00:39:23,083
<font color="#ffff00"><b>His wounds have not fully recovered yet.</b></font>

600
00:39:23,443 --> 00:39:24,283
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Right.</b></font>

601
00:39:26,443 --> 00:39:27,963
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Your wound might get infected this way.</b></font>

602
00:39:30,803 --> 00:39:32,683
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I don't want to be all bandaged up
like a mummy.</b></font>

603
00:39:32,763 --> 00:39:35,403
<font color="#ffff00"><b>-So I...
-But your wound might get infected.</b></font>

604
00:39:35,883 --> 00:39:38,363
<font color="#ffff00"><b>The air is really polluted.
What happens if it scars?</b></font>

605
00:39:42,963 --> 00:39:45,603
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Do you bring this stuff
with you all the time?</b></font>

606
00:39:45,763 --> 00:39:46,763
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Wouldn't you?</b></font>

607
00:39:49,803 --> 00:39:51,803
<font color="#ffff00"><b>So Daoming Si's been discharged already?</b></font>

608
00:39:52,163 --> 00:39:53,003
<font color="#ffff00"><b>That's great.</b></font>

609
00:39:53,963 --> 00:39:55,803
<font color="#ffff00"><b>This is the first time
I've seen Si like that.</b></font>

610
00:39:56,123 --> 00:39:58,443
<font color="#ffff00"><b>We grew up with him
and we're all so surprised.</b></font>

611
00:39:59,923 --> 00:40:01,923
<font color="#ffff00"><b>We can see how much he really likes you.</b></font>

612
00:40:02,283 --> 00:40:03,883
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You can see it too, right?</b></font>

613
00:40:07,963 --> 00:40:09,363
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Come on. I'll put it on for you.</b></font>

614
00:40:13,443 --> 00:40:14,283
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Lei.</b></font>

615
00:40:14,683 --> 00:40:16,643
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I really envy you.</b></font>

616
00:40:17,843 --> 00:40:21,203
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You and Jing shouldn't feel awkward
with each other now, you know?</b></font>

617
00:40:22,243 --> 00:40:25,283
<font color="#ffff00"><b>But I still don't know
how to face him with confidence.</b></font>

618
00:40:27,123 --> 00:40:28,483
<font color="#ffff00"><b>It seems so hard.</b></font>

619
00:40:31,203 --> 00:40:32,203
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Just take it slowly.</b></font>

620
00:40:33,323 --> 00:40:36,203
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You and Si can just take it slowly.
It'll be all right.</b></font>

621
00:40:36,883 --> 00:40:37,723
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Really?</b></font>

622
00:40:39,563 --> 00:40:41,723
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You two seem cozy.</b></font>

623
00:40:47,603 --> 00:40:48,843
<font color="#ffff00"><b>What are you doing?</b></font>

624
00:40:48,923 --> 00:40:50,003
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Stupid boy.</b></font>

625
00:40:50,243 --> 00:40:51,843
<font color="#ffff00"><b>He's helping me put on a Band-Aid.</b></font>

626
00:40:53,203 --> 00:40:54,603
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Didn't you take a sick day?</b></font>

627
00:40:56,003 --> 00:40:58,363
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I got bored sleeping at home.
So I came to school instead.</b></font>

628
00:40:59,083 --> 00:41:02,163
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Your ribs haven't healed, right?
Can you move around like this?</b></font>

629
00:41:02,723 --> 00:41:03,643
<font color="#ffff00"><b>So what?</b></font>

630
00:41:03,803 --> 00:41:05,923
<font color="#ffff00"><b>My ability to recover is just like a dog.</b></font>

631
00:41:08,923 --> 00:41:12,243
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I told you it was just a metaphor.
It's just a figure of speech.</b></font>

632
00:41:12,683 --> 00:41:13,963
<font color="#ffff00"><b>An interesting figure of speech.</b></font>

633
00:41:15,083 --> 00:41:16,723
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Did I ask for your opinion?</b></font>

634
00:41:17,323 --> 00:41:18,363
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I'll get going then.</b></font>

635
00:41:21,683 --> 00:41:23,483
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I didn't tell her what you wanted me to.</b></font>

636
00:41:23,923 --> 00:41:24,923
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Just tell her yourself.</b></font>

637
00:41:26,763 --> 00:41:28,163
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Hey.</b></font>

638
00:41:28,963 --> 00:41:29,803
<font color="#ffff00"><b>What is it?</b></font>

639
00:41:32,243 --> 00:41:34,123
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Do you know what day it is on the 31st?</b></font>

640
00:41:35,403 --> 00:41:36,403
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You don't know?</b></font>

641
00:41:36,643 --> 00:41:38,323
<font color="#ffff00"><b>How dare you? It's my birthday!</b></font>

642
00:41:38,483 --> 00:41:39,363
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Well then.</b></font>

643
00:41:39,643 --> 00:41:41,163
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Happy birthday.</b></font>

644
00:41:41,723 --> 00:41:45,043
<font color="#ffff00"><b>We have a birthday party every year.
You have to bring a gift.</b></font>

645
00:41:45,123 --> 00:41:47,123
<font color="#ffff00"><b>What? How can you act like this?</b></font>

646
00:41:47,203 --> 00:41:48,403
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You even asked for a gift?</b></font>

647
00:41:48,483 --> 00:41:50,403
<font color="#ffff00"><b>-Would you give me a gift if I didn't?
-Of course.</b></font>

648
00:41:52,243 --> 00:41:53,883
<font color="#ffff00"><b>All right. Then bring it.</b></font>

649
00:41:54,203 --> 00:41:56,603
<font color="#ffff00"><b>This is your fault.
You have to make it up to me.</b></font>

650
00:41:56,883 --> 00:41:59,283
<font color="#ffff00"><b>By the way, my mom will be there too.
Wear something nice.</b></font>

651
00:41:59,843 --> 00:42:00,923
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Your mom?</b></font>

652
00:42:01,243 --> 00:42:04,723
<font color="#ffff00"><b>-Your mom would be back from overseas?
-Yes. I'll introduce you to her.</b></font>

